{
  "stem": "19218.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 235.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even though I ran to the factory, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had my prayer book.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember this very vividly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I recited [HEBREW] [SIGHS] in the moonlight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The following day, my father came to the factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, they did not return.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just a rumor that they came back, that they're coming back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, of course, a few days later, the Russians came in and occupied our town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were under the-- on the Russian side of Poland, which was divided into two sections.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One the Germans kept, and we were on the other section.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was there attending Russian school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They called it there the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is, I presume, on the level of high school, but was probably a little bit more strict or more-- the curriculum was a little bit higher than-- than the high school in there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I attended the Russian school for approximately 23 or 21 months in Russian school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It wasn't too bad, with the exception that they have-- for me, as a youngster, it was great.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was only 14 years old at the time in 1939.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And suddenly, I was on an equal basis with everyone-- with everyone else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Polish kids, of course, they always called names-- dirty Jew and everything else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Suddenly the Russians came in, we were supposed to be equal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So as far as I was concerned, as a young boy, I wasn't afraid anymore of the-- of the Polish students, and we were on an equal basis.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "However, I learned very, very fast, of course, since we were-- we owned a factory, we were industrialists supposedly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we were outcasts again, because the Russians didn't like anyone who supposedly was a capitalist.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
